<item>
            <title>[PIG-2066] Accumulators should be able to early-terminate</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2066</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Accumulators are currently forced to process the whole bag; getValue() is called at the very end.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Early termination is a handy feature to be able to use (for IsEmpty, for example).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can add this as a new interface extending Accumulator.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
